-- Dental Center Idea - English-speaking dental clinic in Algarrobo, Málaga
('Dental Center Idea', 'Dentists', 'English-speaking dental clinic located in Algarrobo, Málaga, serving the Costa del Sol area. Provides comprehensive dental care for local residents and international expats with English-speaking staff ensuring clear communication throughout treatments. Services include general dentistry (check-ups, cleanings, fillings, extractions), cosmetic dentistry (teeth whitening, veneers, smile makeovers), restorative dentistry (crowns, bridges, dentures, dental implants), orthodontics (Invisalign and traditional braces), endodontics (root canal treatments), periodontics (gum disease treatment), and pediatric dentistry for children. The clinic offers personalized treatment plans with modern dental technology and emphasizes patient comfort. Emergency dental services available. Conveniently located in Algarrobo with easy access from surrounding areas including Nerja, Torrox, and Vélez-Málaga. Open Monday through Friday with flexible appointment scheduling.', 'Calle San Sebastián, 14, 29750 Algarrobo, Málaga', 'Algarrobo', 'Málaga', '+34 952 550 637', 'info@dentalcenteridea.es', NULL, true, false, true, false, NOW(), NOW());
